{{!
    @template mod_playercross/round_play

    Clue guess forms and the shared virtual keyboard for an active round. The
    mystery-phrase's own guess form lives in mod_playercross/round_panel, not here —
    both share the .mod-playercross-guess-form class so amd/src/game.js can wire click-
    to-activate, per-letter navigation and submission with a single set of delegated
    listeners on #playercross-stage, re-rendered wholesale after every action without
    re-wiring individual listeners.

    Each clue's phrase is always shown — it is the question itself, not an optional
    reveal. Every already-revealed letter of the answer renders as a locked, read-only
    tile (a plain <span>, never focusable); every still-hidden letter renders as its own
    real single-character <input> (inputmode="none", so the device's own on-screen
    keyboard never appears — see the virtual keyboard below). Typing in one of these
    boxes — physically or via the virtual keyboard — advances focus straight to the next
    hidden box, skipping locked ones automatically; clicking a specific box focuses
    exactly that one, letting a mistake be fixed without retyping the rest. Submission
    assembles the full guess by reading every tile in order: a locked span's own letter,
    or a hidden box's typed value.

    No guess form carries a visible submit button — every guess is confirmed via the
    virtual keyboard's own Enviar key (or a physical Enter key), never a separate
    on-screen button. Each form still keeps a `.visually-hidden` submit button so
    screen readers have a discoverable action, even though nothing is painted on screen
    for it.

    The keyboard's own Space key is a no-op here — word boundaries in the mystery
    phrase are structural (each word is its own tile group, see round_panel), not typed,
    and a clue's own word never contains a space regardless.

    Example context (json):
    {
        "clues": [
            {
                "clueid": 12,
                "phrase": "A place to keep notes and school exercises",
                "resolved": false,
                "exhausted": false,
                "attemptsused": 1,
                "revealword": "",
                "tiles": [
                    {"letter": "", "revealed": false, "slotnum": "3", "arialabel": "Hidden letter, slot 3"},
                    {"letter": "A", "revealed": true, "slotnum": "", "arialabel": "A, revealed"}
                ],
                "canguess": true
            },
            {
                "clueid": 13,
                "phrase": "A tool used to write",
                "resolved": true,
                "exhausted": false,
                "attemptsused": 1,
                "revealword": "CANETA",
                "tiles": [],
                "canguess": false
            }
        ],
        "guesslabel": "Your answer",
        "submitclueguess": "Submit",
        "keyboardlabel": "Virtual keyboard",
        "keyboardenterlabel": "Submit",
        "keyboardentertext": "Send",
        "keyboardbackspacelabel": "Delete last letter",
        "keyboardspacelabel": "Space",
        "showcedilla": false
    }
}}
<div id="playercross-round-play">
    <ul id="playercross-clues-list" class="mod-playercross-clues list-unstyled">
        {{#clues}}
            <li class="mod-playercross-clue{{#resolved}} is-resolved{{/resolved}}{{#exhausted}} is-exhausted{{/exhausted}}"
                data-clue-id="{{clueid}}">
                <p class="mod-playercross-clue-phrase">{{phrase}}</p>
                {{#resolved}}
                    <span class="mod-playercross-clue-answer">&#10003; {{revealword}}</span>
                {{/resolved}}
                {{#exhausted}}
                    <span class="text-muted small">{{attemptsused}}</span>
                {{/exhausted}}
                {{#canguess}}
                    <form class="mod-playercross-clue-form mod-playercross-guess-form" data-clue-id="{{clueid}}">
                        <div class="mod-playercross-clue-tiles" data-clue-tiles="{{clueid}}"
                             role="group" aria-label="{{guesslabel}}">
                            {{#tiles}}
                                <div class="mod-playercross-tile-wrap small">
                                    {{#revealed}}
                                        <span class="mod-playercross-tile is-revealed"
                                              aria-label="{{arialabel}}">{{letter}}</span>
                                    {{/revealed}}
                                    {{^revealed}}
                                        <input type="text"
                                               class="mod-playercross-tile mod-playercross-tile-input"
                                               inputmode="none"
                                               autocomplete="off"
                                               maxlength="1"
                                               aria-label="{{arialabel}}"
                                               required>
                                    {{/revealed}}
                                    <span class="mod-playercross-tile-num">{{slotnum}}</span>
                                </div>
                            {{/tiles}}
                        </div>
                        <button type="submit" class="visually-hidden">{{submitclueguess}}</button>
                    </form>
                {{/canguess}}
            </li>
        {{/clues}}
    </ul>

    <div id="playercross-keyboard" class="mod-playercross-keyboard" role="group" aria-label="{{keyboardlabel}}">
        <div class="mod-playercross-keyboard-row">
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="Q" tabindex="-1">Q</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="W" tabindex="-1">W</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="E" tabindex="-1">E</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="R" tabindex="-1">R</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="T" tabindex="-1">T</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="Y" tabindex="-1">Y</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="U" tabindex="-1">U</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="I" tabindex="-1">I</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="O" tabindex="-1">O</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="P" tabindex="-1">P</button>
        </div>
        <div class="mod-playercross-keyboard-row">
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="A" tabindex="-1">A</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="S" tabindex="-1">S</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="D" tabindex="-1">D</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="F" tabindex="-1">F</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="G" tabindex="-1">G</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="H" tabindex="-1">H</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="J" tabindex="-1">J</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="K" tabindex="-1">K</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="L" tabindex="-1">L</button>
            {{#showcedilla}}
                <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="Ç" tabindex="-1">Ç</button>
            {{/showcedilla}}
        </div>
        <div class="mod-playercross-keyboard-row">
            <button type="button"
                    class="pc-key pc-key-wide pc-key-enter"
                    data-key="ENTER"
                    tabindex="-1"
                    aria-label="{{keyboardenterlabel}}">{{keyboardentertext}}</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="Z" tabindex="-1">Z</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="X" tabindex="-1">X</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="C" tabindex="-1">C</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="V" tabindex="-1">V</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="B" tabindex="-1">B</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="N" tabindex="-1">N</button>
            <button type="button" class="pc-key" data-key="M" tabindex="-1">M</button>
            <button type="button"
                    class="pc-key pc-key-wide pc-key-backspace"
                    data-key="BACKSPACE"
                    tabindex="-1"
                    aria-label="{{keyboardbackspacelabel}}">&#x232b;</button>
        </div>
        <div class="mod-playercross-keyboard-row">
            <button type="button"
                    class="pc-key pc-key-space"
                    data-key="SPACE"
                    tabindex="-1"
                    aria-label="{{keyboardspacelabel}}">{{keyboardspacelabel}}</button>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
